<LI><H2>Set of Positive Tuples (Po)
</H2>
<UL>
<LI>Set of Negative Tuples (No)
<LI>Body (Conjunction of Literals) Initialized to True
<LI>Old Variables
</UL></UL><UL>
<LI><H2>Operators:Add a new literal   Preds*(vars+arity-1)*arity
</H2>
<UL>
<LI>Using every predicate, and every way of inserting New and Old Variables
<LI>Produces a Set of Positive Tuples  (P1), Negative Tuples  (N1),  Body, Variables
</UL></UL><UL>
